ke":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f7309b46d37521f0ae4dd7a8be62d644e8898838","tid":752724,"uid":144024,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T08:26:07.000Z","msg":"你地係未借過錢定真係成班數學差到咁？<br />\n<br />\n我當佢分12期係一個月一期。<br />\n實際年利率係3.0%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係1.5%，佢每期還嘅錢會減咗本架。<br />\n<br />\n至於貴唔貴，一啲都唔係貴，（而家3個月HIBOR講緊都2.0689%），即係個loan 講緊係H+0.9311%<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然，唔排除有人可以搵到更平，但算係咁啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T08:38:44.000Z","msg":"心水清，學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上面班友息率都未計到小心中陷阱"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T08:40:16.000Z","msg":"求詳細點解會變左3%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:28:54.000Z","msg":"當我今日借20萬，利息total 3000，如果係一年後一砲過還203,000，咁樣年利率就係1.5%<br />\n<br />\n但而家係instalment，分12期還。<br />\n每期16,916，當息本比率係平分嘅，每個月還咗本16,666，息250。（留意係當咋）<br />\n咁過咗第一個月嘅本只係得返183,334，個本係一路減少，所以你借嘅並唔係借咗200000一年。而只係平均借咗10000一年。利息總共3000，所以實際利率係3%<br />\n<br />\n不過，銀行loan 還款期數係一開始息多本少，後期本多息少，所以實際嘅年利率係比3%低少少嘅。"},{"pid":"f89ca5aa879eecade4c92c744bcf21d5aa4ff3fe","tid":752724,"uid":106165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fdb9cde2a69fbc3c00c912d201ec316ff59f770","tid":752724,"uid":49648,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:08:56.000Z","msg":"渣打來的，乜都唔駛搞，諗梗要來做咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:30:54.000Z","msg":"兩個鐘前都有打黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a84a1